en.title: FE Presents Quantum Science Products to HRH Prince Norodom Chakrapong of Cambodia!
en.content: FE's Thailand Country Licensee and Presidential Director Don Chan recently visited Cambodia and presented FE's Quantum Science products to HRH Prince Norodom Chakrapong of Cambodia. Prince Norodom is the High Privy Advisor to his Majesty the King of Cambodia. HRH Prince Norodom is highly impressed by FE's Quantum Science products and FE's principle of compassion which has helped many less fortunate of society to lead a better life.
